channel.title: My God Sword From Scratch
channel.description:
I finished my god sword from scratch, and its actually 3d on the top, i didnt to this:
Draw - then Select - Copy - Paste - Move away abit - Connect the lines.
If i did that, it would be flat on top.
So... i acutally made it 3d on top, instead of flat. Here are some pics
[img]http://img12.imageshack.us/img12/7615/render1k.png[/img] [img]http://img12.imageshack.us/img12/8967/render2c.png[/img] [img]http://img12.imageshack.us/img12/117/89388966.png[/img]
Tell me what you think
